Here is the solution:   Add a <code><div style="clear:left;margin-top:22px"></div></code> before the <code>.last</code> element*  Add <code>margin-top: -22px;</code> to <code>.last</code> where the amount is about the same as the line-height  If you dont want it to get too small add <code>min-width</code> to <code>.last</code> and it will work as you'd expect Also <code>min-width: 1px;</code> is requiered in the class to avoid it getting 0 in special cases.   Tested and working in IE8+, Edge, Chrome, Opera, Firefox    <code>* { box-sizing: border-box; }
