I am trying to implement HTML/CSS where there are four list items ( <code>li</code> ) within a full-width unordered list element ( <code>ul</code> ), but am struggling to get one of those items to use the <code>text-overflow:ellipsis</code> command.  The result should be something along these lines...  <code>+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
