Comments  This answer I am giving does not work with floats. Instead I am using the more modern CSS3 solution ( so watch out with browser compatability ) using display:flex. Flex offers a lot more easy options for future edits as well. It also resizes the height of all divs on a line to be the same height and probably a few more things ^^.  JSFiddle (resize the width in JSFiddle to see the effect)  HTML  <code><div class="wrap">
